Package: libdballe-bin
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends} ${misc:Depends}
Description: swiss-army knife for CREX-encoded meteorological data
 dballetool provides various miscellaneous utility functions for working with
 meteorological data encoded in WMO FM 95 CREX format.
 .
 Currently implemented are:
  * dump the contents of a CREX message
  * expand CREX B and D table entries
